---
import CustomImage from '@/components/CustomImage'
import ImageCarousel from '@/components/ImageCarousel'
import CardCarousel from '@/components/CardCarousel'
import StickyHeader from '@/components/StickyHeader'
import BaseLayout from '@/layouts/BaseLayout'

const SITE_TITLE = 'Descheeto'
---

<BaseLayout title={SITE_TITLE}>
	<StickyHeader
		title='Descheeto'
		buyUrl='https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=2949961654'
		buyLabel='Subscribe on the Workshop'
		exploreLabel='Tech Specs'
		exploreUrl='#specs'
	/>
	<div>
		<h1 class='title text-6xl font-bold'>{SITE_TITLE}</h1>
		<h2 class='text-3xl font-medium mt-4 mb-10'>Like Nothing Else</h2>
		<CustomImage
			imagePath='/src/assets/images/stormworks/descheeto/hero.jpg'
			altText='Like Nothing Else'
		/>
		<div class='flex justify-center mt-10'>
			<div
				class='w-fit px-4 py-1.5 text-sm rounded-full bg-sky-500 hover:bg-sky-600 text-white font-medium transition-colors'
			>
				<a href='https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=2949961654' target='_blank'
					>Subscribe on the Workshop</a
				>
			</div>
		</div>

		<article class='prose prose-xl dark:prose-invert w-full max-w-none mt-8'>
			<p>
				Descheeto is a bus fit for a player. Welcome to the future of mass transportation. Descheeto
				has been completely redesigned from the ground up, ready to deliver an experience like no
				other. With all-wheel-steering, an immensely powerful engine, SenCar 5, luxury coach cabin,
				and much more, it is the crown jewel in a SentyTek fleet of buses.
			</p>

			<h2>Design</h2>
			<p>
				The design of the Descheeto is a true masterpiece of engineering and artistry. From its
				sleek painted exterior to its luxurious interior, every detail has been carefully crafted to
				provide the ultimate transportation experience. The new paint job, which we call "Coastal",
				is a showstopper, providing a welcoming entrance, but not distracting other drivers. The
				dual-supercharged 27 cylinder engine is not only powerful but also eco-friendly, making the
				Descheeto a smart choice for those who care about the environment.
			</p>
			<CustomImage
				imagePath='/src/assets/images/stormworks/descheeto/ext-r.jpg'
				altText='The sleek exterior design of the Descheeto, with its new Coastal paint job'
			/>
			<p>
				The redesigned cabin is a marvel of comfort and style. The new luxury seats are designed to
				provide maximum comfort, with plenty of legroom and adjustable headrests. The realistic
				lighting system creates a warm and inviting atmosphere, while the state-of-the-art
				entertainment system ensures that passengers are entertained and connected throughout their
				journey. Descheeto truly represents the future of transportation, where form and function
				combine to create an unforgettable experience for passengers.
			</p>

			<h2>Interior</h2>
			<p>
				The interior of the Descheeto is a sanctuary of comfort and luxury. The SenCar 5 powered
				dashboard is a technological marvel, providing drivers with all the essential information
				they need to operate the bus safely and efficiently. The dashboard features a
				high-resolution display that provides real-time data on everything from fuel levels to
				engine performance. The new slide-out driver seat is designed to give drivers easy access to
				essential equipment, so they can focus on the road ahead.
			</p>
			<CustomImage
				imagePath='/src/assets/images/stormworks/descheeto/int-super.jpg'
				altText='The driver seat of the Descheeto, featuring the new slide-out design and the SenCar 5 dashboard'
			/>
			<p>
				The new luxury seats are designed to provide the utmost comfort, with premium materials and
				ergonomic features to support passengers on even the longest journeys. The interior of the
				Descheeto is the perfect combination of form and function, providing a luxurious and
				comfortable experience for passengers, while also offering the latest technology and
				features for drivers.
			</p>
			<CustomImage
				imagePath='/src/assets/images/stormworks/descheeto/int-rear.jpg'
				altText='The luxurious interior of the Descheeto, featuring the new dashboard and slide-out driver seat'
			/>

			<h2>SenCar 5</h2>
			<p>
				SenCar 5 is the successor to the powerful car operating system, SenTOS Car 4. SenCar 5
				enhances your car with all new personalization features, seemless communication methods, a
				brand new UI, drive modes, and more. SenCar 5 features a brand new UI, made from scratch,
				with as little compromises as possible. There are 4 new screens, 2 are optional, for a full
				new experience of using SenCar 5, and any car it is in. SenCar 5 is designed to take over
				nearly every element of a car, and the 4 new screens let you control them perfectly. Built
				on top of the powerful SenOS architecture, it is easier than ever to control a car now.
			</p>
			<p>
				SenCar 5 features 7 themes to customize your experience with the car to the max. Custom
				currated colors match each theme perfectly, so that they dont contrast eachother.
			</p>
			<CustomImage
				imagePath='/src/assets/images/stormworks/descheeto/int-wide.jpg'
				altText='The new SenCar 5 interface, showing the different themes and the new dashboard layout'
			/>
			<p>
				SenCar 5 features 4 drive modes to elevate your driving experience: Eco mode, Sport mode,
				Tow mode, and Downhill Assist mode. Eco mode resists downshifting and encourages upshifting
				to keep the RPMs low. Sport mode does the complete opposite. Tow mode increases torque and
				adds Traction Control. Downhill Assist keeps the speed low, feathers the clutch, and keeps
				braking high. These new drive modes are perfect for navigating the existing world of
				Stormworks, with its combination of steep challenging mountains, flatlands, and light hills.
			</p>

			<h2>SenConnect</h2>
			<p>
				First debuted on the Descheeto in 2021, SenConnect is our incredible P2P communcation
				standard for showing other SenConnect vehicles on the map. Now, the Moraine has SenConnect,
				and with SenCar 5, other vehicles with SenConnect show up directly on the dashboard map.
				It's really easy to see where your friends are without going into the game map now.
			</p>
			<CustomImage
				imagePath='/src/assets/images/stormworks/descheeto/sc.jpg'
				altText='The SenConnect system showing other vehicles on the map, with a closeup of the dashboard'
			/>

			<h2 id='specs'>Specs</h2>
			<table>
				<tbody>
					<tr>
						<th>Engine</th>
						<td>27cyl dual-supercharged 1x1</td>
					</tr>
					<tr>
						<th>Transmission</th>
						<td>5 speed AutoManual</td>
					</tr>
					<tr>
						<th>OS</th>
						<td>SenCar 5 with SiBTaT</td>
					</tr>
					<tr>
						<th>ECU</th>
						<td>RECO 1.3</td>
					</tr>
					<tr>
						<th>Top Speed</th>
						<td>110mph/180kph</td>
					</tr>
				</tbody>
			</table>

			<CustomImage
				imagePath='/src/assets/images/stormworks/descheeto/wide.jpg'
				altText='Descheeto parked at a bus stop'
			/>
		</article>
	</div>
</BaseLayout>

<script>
	import { animate } from 'motion'
	const showAnimations = localStorage.getItem('animations') === 'true'

	if (showAnimations) {
		animate(
			'.title',
			{ y: [80, 0], opacity: [0, 1] },
			{
				duration: 2.5,
				opacity: { duration: 3 },

				offset: [0, 0.55, 0.75]
			}
		)
	}
</script>
